Buffer service routine
#Parent Buffer_
=>	R0 =	reason code
	 	0 <insert byte=>Buffer_service0>
	 	1 <insert block=>Buffer_service1>
	 	2 <remove byte=>Buffer_service2>
	 	3 <remove block=>Buffer_service3>
	 	4 <examine byte=>Buffer_service4>
	 	5 <examine block=>Buffer_service5>
	 	6 <return used space=>Buffer_service6>
	 	7 <return free space=>Buffer_service7>
	 	8 <purge=>Buffer_service8>
	 	9 <next filled block=>Buffer_service9>

These calls modify a buffer.